*Data Selection:* Retrieve data where {color:#ff5630}type_of_scrape = ‘01_days_out’{color}

*Effective Start Date:* 1st day of the current month

*Effective End Date:* Three months from the start date, through the end of that month

{color:#bf2600}*Purpose*{color}*:* Serve as forecast rates

h3. {color:#0747a6}Daily Rate Values{color}

Continue to run daily in addition to the Master Rates daily run

Retrieve data where ype_of_scrape = ‘00_days_out’

