column28:
When booking a New Zealand customer for a hire, we are receiving an error from RentCentric when calling CreateRes API. The error states the field CountryCode has a maximum of 10 characters. However the New Zealand country is 11 characters.  Please ensure the field is updated to cater for all country names (e.g. 50 characters) since it’s expecting strings and not a code.

Original request data from Reclaim: [^1764125817148.dat] 

RentCentric response:

{noformat}{
  "Status": "NotFound",
  "Code": 404,
  "ErrorMessage": "Entity of type &quot;Customer&quot; in state &quot;Modified&quot; has the following validation errors: - Property: &quot;CountryCode&quot;, Error: &quot;The field CountryCode must be a string or array type with a maximum length of &#39;10&#39;.&quot;",
  "Result": null
}{noformat}

