column28:
For the “Source of Business” field in reservation, the following are expected:

# If file generated from the Partner Portal when Reservation Type = Corporate, “Corporate Web Direct” will be populated;
# If file generated by user manually when Reservation Type = Corporate, “Corporate Inbound Call” will be populated;
# If file generated by the Direct Website when Reservation Type = Direct, “Direct Web Direct” will be populated;
# If file generated by user manually when Reservation Type = Direct, “Direct Inbound Call” will be populated.

